    <div class="well">
      The <strong>Bankmybiz Network</strong> can answer your business questions and match you with local and national sources of capital.
    </div>
    <h3 class='text-center'>Testimonials</h3>
    <div class="well">
      <section>
        <i>"I sent messages to my Bankmybiz lender matches and within 2 mintues was contacted by a lender from California who understood and was passionate about my business. Thanks Bankmybiz!"</i>
        <p class='text-right'><strong>Alisa T.</strong> Artist/Manufacturer</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <i>"Wow, Bankmybiz.com is extraordinary. Easy to navigate, engaging interactions and spot-on connections. <strong>This will change everything</strong>."</i>
        <p class='text-right'><strong>James C.</strong> SVP Business Banker</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <i>"I started conversations by posting some questions to Bankmybiz.com. I connected with a few helpful lenders and, <strong>EUREKA</strong>, I found a great lender who specialized in my industry. Thank You Bankmybiz.com! I will be singing your praises to every business owner I know."</i>
        <p class='text-right'><strong>Heather P.</strong> Healthcare</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <%= render 'shared/social_buttons' %>
  <%= render 'shared/user_tags' %>
